Package: window-transparency
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-gi, xdotool, x11-utils
Recommends: gir1.2-keybinder-3.0
Maintainer: Mounstroya
Description: System tray tool to control active window transparency on X11
 Allows toggling and adjusting the transparency of the active window
 directly from the system tray. Supports presets, per-application rules,
 custom opacity levels, and an optional global keyboard shortcut.
